          "year": 2026,
          "note": "Sean breaks down the new trailer for Spielberg's next before interviewing him at South by Southwest. Josh O'Connor plays an Edward Snowden-style whistleblower, and Colin Firth appears via bio-virtual tech. Colman Domingo plays the truth-teller, and the film reads as a first-contact story recast for an age of government distrust."
